#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, "
"floppy and &CD; drives, USB sticks &etc;) along with information on their "
"capacity, free space, type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and "
"unmount drives and view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; prikaže razpoložljive datotečne naprave (particije trdega diska, "
"diskete in diske, ključke USB &etc;) skupaj z informacijami o njihovi "
"zmogljivosti, prostem prostoru, vrsti in priključni točki. Omogoča tudi "
"priklop in odklop diskov ter njihov ogled v upravitelju datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdiskfree; is similar to the &systemsettings; Storage Devices module, but "
"takes up less screen space. It is useful if you want to keep a &kdiskfree; "
"window available at all times."
msgstr ""
"&kdiskfree; je podoben &systemsettings; Modul Storage Devices, vendar "
"zavzame manj prostora na zaslonu. Uporabno je, če želite ohranjati okno "
"&kdiskfree; na voljo ves čas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "Zagon &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> at a command prompt or "
"select <guimenuitem>KDiskFree</guimenuitem> from the <guisubmenu>System</"
"guisubmenu> group in the application launcher. The standard &Qt; and &kde; "
"command options are available, and can be listed by entering "
"<userinput><command>kdf</command> <option>--help</option></userinput> at the "
"command prompt."
msgstr ""
"V ukazno vrstico vnesite <userinput><command>kdf</command></userinput> ali "
"izberite <guimenuitem>KDiskFree</guimenuitem> iz skupine <guisubmenu>Sistem</"
"guisubmenu> v zaganjalniku programa. Na voljo so standardne možnosti ukazov "
"&Qt; in &kde;, ki jih lahko naštejete z vnosom <userinput><command>kdf</"
"command> <option>--help</option></userinput> v ukazno vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To run the application as an applet in the systemtray, use "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in application launcher."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aplikacijo zagnati kot applet v sistemskem predalu, uporabite "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Sistem</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>KwikDisk</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> v zaganjalniku aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The features of &kdiskfree; are also available in the &systemsettings; "
"module <guilabel>Storage Devices</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Funkcije &kdiskfree; so na voljo tudi v modulu &systemsettings; "
"<guilabel>Naprave za shranjevanje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main window"
msgstr "Glavno okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "The main &kdiskfree; window displays the available file devices."
msgstr "The main &kdiskfree; window displays the available file devices."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Normally, the following pieces of information are included:"
msgstr "Običajno so vključeni naslednji podatki:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kdiskfree; Zaslon</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kdiskfree; Zaslon</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "an icon depicting the type of storage"
msgstr "ikona, ki označuje vrsto shranjevanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "device name"
msgstr "ime naprave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid "filesystem type"
msgstr "vrsta datotečnega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "total size"
msgstr "skupna velikost"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "mount point"
msgstr "priklopna točka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "free disk space"
msgstr "prosti prostor na disku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "the percentage of space used as a number and as a graph."
msgstr "odstotek uporabljenega prostora v obliki števila in grafa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton> clicking on the header of a particular "
"column sorts the devices according to that variable. A second "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click sorts in the opposite order."
msgstr ""
"<mousebutton>Levi</mousebutton> klik na glavo določenega stolpca razvrsti "
"naprave glede na to spremenljivko. Drugi <mousebutton>levi</mousebutton> "
"klik razvrsti v nasprotnem vrstnem redu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking with the &RMB; on a row pops up a menu. If that device is not "
"currently mounted, the <guimenuitem>Mount Device</guimenuitem> option is "
"available. If the device is mounted, it can be unmounted by choosing "
"<guimenuitem>Unmount Device</guimenuitem>. Selecting <guimenuitem>Open in "
"File Manager</guimenuitem> opens a new window with a graphical view of the "
"files on that device."
msgstr ""
"S klikom z &RMB; na vrstico se odpre meni. Če ta naprava trenutno ni "
"priklopljena, je na voljo možnost <guimenuitem>Priklopi napravo</"
"guimenuitem>. Če je naprava nameščena, jo lahko odstranite z izbiro "
"<guimenuitem>Odklopi Napravo</guimenuitem>. Z izbiro možnosti "
"<guimenuitem>Odpri v upravitelju datotek</guimenuitem> se odpre novo okno z "
"grafičnim prikazom datotek v tej napravi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The setting for the file manager used by &kdiskfree; is independent from the "
"choice in the &systemsettings; module <guilabel>Default Applications</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev upravitelja datotek, ki ga uporablja &kdiskfree;, je neodvisna od "
"izbire v modulu &systemsettings; <guilabel>Privzete aplikacije</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Bar and Configuration"
msgstr "Menijska vrstica in konfiguracija"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni za datoteke"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Update</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Posodobi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Immediately updates the display to reflect the current status"
msgstr "Takoj posodobi zaslon, da odraža trenutno stanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izhod</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Closes</action> &kdiskfree;"
msgstr "<action>Zapre</action> &kdiskfree;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kdiskfree; has some common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read the "
"sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings"
"\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega ima &kdiskfree; nekatere skupne elemente menija &kde; "
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu>, za več informacij "
"preberite poglavja o <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-"
"settings\">Menij Nastavitve</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Menij Pomoč</ulink> v &kde; Osnovah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Nastavitve"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija &kdiskfree; Zaslon</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Configure &kdiskfree; Screen</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfigurirajte &kdiskfree; Zaslon</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This dialog has two tabbed windows, <guilabel>General Settings</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Mount Commands</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"To pogovorno okno ima dva zavihka: <guilabel>Splošne nastavitve</guilabel> "
"in <guilabel>Ukazi za Priklop</guilabel>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Splošne nastavitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the word <guilabel>visible</guilabel> or <guilabel>hidden</"
"guilabel> to turn display of an data field on or off."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na besedo <guilabel>vidno</guilabel> ali <guilabel>skrito</"
"guilabel>, da vklopite ali izklopite prikaz podatkovnega polja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Change the update frequency by editing the value. The value in the box is "
"the interval (in seconds) between updates of the &kdiskfree; display to "
"reflect the current status."
msgstr ""
"Z urejanjem vrednosti spremenite pogostost posodabljanja. Vrednost v polju "
"je interval (v sekundah) med posodobitvami prikaza &kdiskfree;, ki odraža "
"trenutno stanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>File Manager</guilabel> setting controls the command executed "
"when the <guimenuitem>Open Filemanager</guimenuitem> popup menu item is "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitev <guilabel>Upravitelj datotek</guilabel> nadzoruje ukaz, ki se "
"izvede, ko je izbrana postavka <guimenuitem>Odpri upravitelj datotek</"
"guimenuitem> v priročnem meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are also two check boxes. One controls if a file manager window will "
"be automatically opened when a device is mounted. The other causes an alert "
"window to pop up if a disk gets critically full."
msgstr ""
"Na voljo sta tudi dve potrditveni polji. Eno določa, ali se bo ob priključku "
"naprave samodejno odprlo okno upravitelja datotek. Drugo povzroči, da se ob "
"kritični polnosti diska prikaže opozorilno okno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mount Commands"
msgstr "Priključni ukazi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows the user to specify the mount and unmount commands for a given "
"device, as well as the icon used to represent it. More information on these "
"commands can be found on the man page for <application>mount</application> "
"(type <userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></userinput> "
"at the command prompt)."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniku omogoča, da določi ukaze za priklop in odklop določene naprave "
"ter ikono, ki jo predstavlja. Več informacij o teh ukazih najdete na strani "
"man za <application>mount</application> (v ukazni vrstici vnesite "
"<userinput><command>man</command> <option>mount</option></userinput>)."

